ne\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* waline 评论系统关键部分，不然会出现提示框均在同一位置的问题 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.wl-header</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">overflow</span>: visible;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.wl-header-item</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">position</span>: relative;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* end */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.wl-header-item</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:nth-child</span>(<span class=\"number\">1</span>)<span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:before</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">content</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;输入QQ号会自动获取昵称和头像🐧&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.wl-header-item</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:nth-child</span>(<span class=\"number\">2</span>)<span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:before</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">content</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;收到回复将通过的邮箱提醒您📧&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.wl-header-item</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:nth-child</span>(<span class=\"number\">3</span>)<span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:before</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">content</span>: <span class=\"string\">&#x27;可以通过昵称访问您的网站🔗&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.wl-header-item</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:focus-within</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">::before</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">display</span>: block;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* 主内容区 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.wl-header-item</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">::before</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">display</span>: none;             <span class=\"comment\">/* 先隐藏起来 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">position</span>: absolute;        <span class=\"comment\">/* 绝对定位 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">top</span>: -<span class=\"number\">31px</span>;                <span class=\"comment\">/* 向上移动60像素 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">white-space</span>: nowrap;       <span class=\"comment\">/* 文字强制不换行，防止left:50%导致的文字换行 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">border-radius</span>: <span class=\"number\">10px</span>;       <span class=\"comment\">/* 圆角 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">left</span>: <span class=\"number\">50%</span>;                 <span class=\"comment\">/* 距离左边50% */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">transform</span>: <span class=\"built_in\">translate</span>(-<span class=\"number\">50%</span>);<span class=\"comment\">/* 然后再向左边挪动自身的一半，即可实现居中 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">/* 填充 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">padding</span>: <span class=\"number\">0px</span> <span class=\"number\">18px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">background</span>: <span class=\"number\">#669900</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"number\">#fff</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"更多\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#更多\"></a> 更多</h1>\n<p>如果想要实现下图效果，可参见文章 <a href=\"https://blog.leonus.cn/2022/inputAlert.html\">给你的评论添加一个输入提醒吧 | Leonus</a></p>\n<p><img src= \"/image/loading.gif\" data-lazy-src=\"https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/20230711235642.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<p>（图源原文）</p>\n<p>其他 Waline 评论区美化教程：<a class=\"uuanqin-bilink\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/p/dd188b35/\"><span class=\"bilink-pop-up\">站内文章</span>【索引】定制自己的 Waline 评论系统</a></p>\n","raw":"---\ntitle: 为评论系统增加输入提醒【Waline】\ntags:\n  - Waline\n  - CSS\ncategories:\n  - 博客站点维护\n  - Waline\nabbrlink: b3be711f\ncover: 'https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/promptcover.webp'\ndescription: 通过CSS设置实现信息输入提示。\ndate: 2023-07-11 23:42:59\ntop_img:\n---\n\n> [!success] 本文已收录至 [Butterfly 主题美化教程](https://butterfly.zhheo.com/)\n\n文章参考自 Leonus 文章 [给你的评论添加一个输入提醒吧 | Leonus](https://blog.leonus.cn/2022/inputAlert.html)，文章原文的实现方案是针对于**Twikoo**评论系统的。本文以此为灵感摸索出针对**Waline**评论系统的实现方案。\n\n> 在这里再次感谢 [Leonus](https://blog.leonus.cn/) 的优质教程以及对我实践过程中的疑惑解答！❤❤❤\n\n# 效果\n\n![img](https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/202410250026177.webp)\n\n# 操作\n\n**Twikoo** 评论系统实现方案参见 Leonus 的文章：[给你的评论添加一个输入提醒吧 | Leonus](https://blog.leonus.cn/2022/inputAlert.html)。\n\n下文将介绍 **Waline** 评论系统的实现方案。\n\n引入以下 CSS：\n\n```css\n/* waline 评论系统关键部分，不然会出现提示框均在同一位置的问题 */\n\n.wl-header {\n    overflow: visible;\n}\n.wl-header-item {\n    position: relative;\n}\n\n/* end */\n\n.wl-header-item:nth-child(1):before {\n    content: '输入QQ号会自动获取昵称和头像🐧';\n}\n\n.wl-header-item:nth-child(2):before {\n    content: '收到回复将通过的邮箱提醒您📧';\n}\n\n.wl-header-item:nth-child(3):before {\n    content: '可以通过昵称访问您的网站🔗';\n}\n\n.wl-header-item:focus-within::before{\n    display: block;\n}\n\n/* 主内容区 */\n.wl-header-item::before {\n    display: none;             /* 先隐藏起来 */\n    position: absolute;        /* 绝对定位 */\n    top: -31px;                /* 向上移动60像素 */\n    white-space: nowrap;       /* 文字强制不换行，防止left:50%导致的文字换行 */\n    border-radius: 10px;       /* 圆角 */\n    left: 50%;                 /* 距离左边50% */\n    transform: translate(-50%);/* 然后再向左边挪动自身的一半，即可实现居中 */\n    /* 填充 */\n    padding: 0px 18px;\n    background: #669900;\n    color: #fff;\n}\n```\n\n# 更多\n\n如果想要实现下图效果，可参见文章 [给你的评论添加一个输入提醒吧 | Leonus](https://blog.leonus.cn/2022/inputAlert.html)\n\n![image.png](https://cdn.gallery.uuanqin.top/img/20230711235642.png)\n\n（图源原文）\n\n其他 Waline 评论区美化教程：[[【索引】定制自己的 Waline 评论系统]]\n","categories":[{"name":"博客站点维护","api":"api/categories/博客站点维护.json"},{"name":"Waline","api":"api/categories/博客站点维护/Waline.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CSS","api":"api/tags/CSS.json"},{"name":"Waline","api":"api/tags/Waline.json"}]},"api":"api/posts/p/b3be711f.json"}